{
  "stem": "7358.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it used to be the German policy, whenever they came into a house and someone was sick, they would kill the person and burn the house because they was always afraid of typhus, or all type of terrible diseases of that nature.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she, not knowing what to say-- he says-- he went in and took a look at me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says to her, who is this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she said, this is my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's sick.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But since he seduced her in the kitchen, I could hear the commotion that I suppose.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he actually asked her-- because he spoke to her in German and a little Polish, and I could understand-- that she should come to visit him, that he was stationed in a small town on the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he like, on good terms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very satisfied, very happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he didn't kill me, didn't burn the house, and I remained.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when my uncle returned back like, a few hours later-- once the Germans had left the village-- my uncle and my aunt returned to see what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The woman was in such hysterics that she said that if they don't take me out of-- if they don't remove me from the house, that-- I don't know what she said she would do.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just couldn't take it, and she was crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was completely-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She screamed for hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my uncle didn't know what to do with me at this point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they had to take me out of the house on short notice, lie, and there was a place in the woods that Jewish people used to hide, say, a year ago, maybe, or eight months ago.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Germans already knew about this place.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
